name: Welcome to manurs github page
tagline: The idea is to show here a little description of my repos
body:
# www.github.com/manurs

***

***

### dotfiles

www.github.com/manurs/dotfiles

I don't use it to much dotfiles, but take a look at .bashrc or .conkyrc

If you don't know about dotfiles just visit internet ;)

***

### Libs in C

www.github.com/manurs/libs

 - StrUtil: use with caution, I made it in my 1 year.
 - Conexion: TCP and SSL stuff. Use with caution could have errors/vulnerabilities.
 - Daemonizar: make your program a daemon.
 - Lib semaforos: manage your semaphores easily.
 - Linked list: elems can be whatever struct you want.

***

### Neuron models

www.github.com/manurs/neuron-models

Diferent libs to work with neuron models, hybrid circuits and closed-loop technologies.
COMEDI, RTAI.

***

### Neural net lib

www.github.com/manurs/neural-net

Lib to create neural networks (you can manage, layers, change activation funtions, etc)

***

### Neuro-genetico

www.github.com/manurs/neurogenetico

Java Machine Learning platform (neural networks, genetic algorithms, kmeans, knn)

***

### Compiler

www.github.com/manurs/compiler

A little compiler.

Can be useful to learn how compilers works.

Including:
 - Symbol table: just global and local zones.
 - Hash: used by symbol table. Can be adapted changing the struct and functions (is not struct independet, by this is not including in libs). 
 - Lexical analyzer.
 - Parser.
 - Code generation.

***

### Search Algorithms

www.github.com/manurs/search_algorithms

Search algorithms.

Also are include tools to generate the dictionaries, measure the times or plot the results.

***

### Python ejers

www.github.com/manurs/python-ejers

Just a few algorithms in python

***

### Rogue Castle

Game page https://manurs.github.io/RogueCastle

GitHub page www.github.com/manurs/RogueCastle

Video game developed with phaser

***

### Android connect 4

https://github.com/manurs/android-connect4

Android app to play connect 4.
